description:
Chaos, confusion, a worldwide pandemic - many people are becoming spiritually awakened and are pondering - "Are we near the end?" Jesus knew His followers would wonder this, and so He provided specific signs that would reveal that His return was near! In this video, we will consider those signs, and consider the world around us to see which have been fulfilled and how close we are to the end of time!
